#, no-wrap
msgid "Wrapping Up"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/docs/guides/security/pam.md:350
msgid ""
"By now, you should have a much better idea of what PAM can do, and how to "
"make changes when needed. However, we must reiterate the importance of being "
"very, *very* careful with any changes you make to PAM modules. You could "
"lock yourself out of your system, or worse, let everyone else in."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ../src/docs/guides/security/pam.md:351
msgid ""
"We would strongly recommend testing all changes in an environment that can "
"be easily reverted to a previous configuration. That said, have fun with it!"
msgstr ""
